body:
FolderDialog force exit dialog

FolderDialog tree remove elements fix

Fix https://github.com/tonikelope/megabasterd/issues/375

Trying to mitigate https://github.com/tonikelope/megabasterd/issues/310

Fix new download menu disabled after empty url set

Fixed (finally) a very old performance problem when loading very very large folders.

VERY BIG FOLDER example -> https://github.com/tonikelope/megabasterd/issues/416

New languages:

Italian ( Thanks to https://github.com/bovirus )
Turkish ( Thanks to https://github.com/FabrieI )
Chinese ( Thanks to https://github.com/linkea131 )

The behavior of the CLEAR ALL FINISHED button has changed. It now removes EVERYTHING that has finished (successfully or with error). In addition, a new menu item has been added that allows to CANCEL ALL DOWNLOADS (both those in standby and those that are active).
Added support for links pointing directly to a file within a folder.

Section 16 of MEGA Terms of Service https://mega.nz/terms specifies that it is mandatory to have a API KEY to use its API. FOR NOW IT IS OPTIONAL IN MEGABASTERD BUT IN THE FUTURE IT WILL BE MANDATORY. Sorry for the inconvenience, but we must "play" according to MEGA rules.

https://mega.nz/sdk
![alt text](https://raw.githubusercontent.com/tonikelope/megabasterd/master/src/main/resources/images/apikey.png)

-swinginvoke in constructors -> less RC
-DL CHUNK SIZE 20MB -> Increased average download speed
-SmartProxy bad proxy block time 120 sec -> 90 sec
-Default font noto
-Default zoom 80%

Let's dance

WARNING: Older downloads are NOT compatible with this version because of the chunk size change. Finish what you are downloading before upgrading.

It's recommended to reset MegaBasterd
   
    RUN NEW VERSION AND IMPORT SETTINGS FROM PREVIOUS VERSION.   

    EXPORT YOUR SETTINGS.

    RESET MEGABASTERD in order to clean transferences internal database (you will lose your transferences (temp files will be preserved)).

    IMPORT SETTINGS

Note: copy and paste your current transfers links in a txt file before RESET.
Note: MegaBasterdWindowsJRE_6.54.zip is a Windows (32/64 bits) portable version.

If HTTP error 509 (download limit reached) occurs, MegaBasterd will attempt to continue the download using the SmartProxy module. 

It is important to note that the download speed using proxies is very variable and depends on multiple factors outside of MegaBasterd. I can't do anything to improve that.

I hope as always, that it will be useful, but if you need a higher download limit at maximum speed I advise you to get a MEGA account.

PS: I'm looking for a collaborator to help me write the MegaBasterd wiki. ( I can't pay you with money, but I'll put you in the credits window :P )

In this version the structure of the internal database of MegaBasterd has changed. In order to keep the settings and accounts configured, it is necessary to EXPORT them from version 6.4 and IMPORT them in version 6.5 (DO NOT JUST REPLACE megabasterd.db new file with the old!).
FINISH TRANSFERENCES WITH PREVIOUS VERSION BEFORE UPDATE.

WARNING: starting with this version, the configuration file will be in $HOME/.megabasterdVERSION/megabasterd.db

If you have a configuration file from a previous version:

OPTION A:
1) Run MegaBasterd 6.1 and exit.

2) Replace the fresh new megabasterd.db with your megabasterd.db old file.

OPTION B:
Export your settings from the previous version and import them from the new version.
